<p class="govuk-body">This is the <a class="govuk-link" href="https://design-system.service.gov.uk/components/header/">GOV.UK header</a> with an extra part to let the user sign out of a service.</p>

<h2 id="when-not-to-use" class="govuk-heading-l">When to use</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">Use this version of the GOV.UK header when the user is signed in to a service, to enable them to sign out.</p>

<h2 id="when-not-to-use" class="govuk-heading-l">When not to use</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">Do not use when the service does not require the user to sign in, or when they are already signed out. Use the default <a class="govuk-link" href="https://design-system.service.gov.uk/components/header/">GOV.UK header</a> instead.</p>

